highlights.text: “All I Want for Christmas Is You” by Mariah Carey is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 82 spots at #82.
“Échame La Culpa” by Luis Fonsi and Demi Lovato is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #13.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 48 weeks straight.
Ozuna has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Criminal” is the highest at #21.
